The '''All Science Research Academy''' was a prestigious school on the world of [[Yerphonia]]. As a young man, [[Granta Omega]] attended the school, with the sponsorship of [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Sano Sauro]]. Omega graduated from the academy a short time before the [[Battle of Naboo/Legends|Battle of Naboo]].

